issues.description: Duplicate 'link' entry in globalQueryParams Set. This could lead to unexpected behavior when processing query parameters.

Critical bug in cacheIndex construction: Template literal uses 'match[0]' as a literal string instead of accessing the match[0] variable value. This will cause cache misses for all requests, defeating the caching mechanism.
Fixed bug: Changed 'data.state === null' to 'json.state === null', indicating the original code was referencing the wrong variable, which could have caused incorrect badge rendering.
